    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SeverLink</strong> 是一款以任务为基础的第三人称 3D 潜行动作游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潜行 (STEALTH):</strong><br>潜入高度戒备的设施，不被发现，获取目标物品后安全离开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动作 (ACTION):</strong><br>当计划失败时，自主决定应对策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互动 (INTERACTION):</strong><br>利用环境优势扭转局面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>调查 (INVESTIGATION):</strong><br>收集情报，分析线索，揭开隐藏的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/a9f04c9dd892dada2701dfed7b4d4219.poster.avif?t=1769712918\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/a9f04c9dd892dada2701dfed7b4d4219.webm?t=1769712918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/a9f04c9dd892dada2701dfed7b4d4219.mp4?t=1769712918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1769712918\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1769712918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1769712918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事设定在201X年，一场改变世界的千年虫危机导致科技发展陷入停滞，游戏因此呈现出受千禧年初硬件与文化影响的复古未来主义美学。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的主角——“潜行者”——将执行一系列任务，每个任务都发生在独特的手工打造场景中，充满专属的挑战与秘密：在疾驰列车上解救告密者，悄然潜入亿万富豪的游艇，或是破袭戒备森严的阿尔卑斯山掩体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他的身后站着KVASIR集团——一个由研究员、黑客与行动派组成的团队，他们不惜一切手段反抗企业强权。不妨将其理解为“配备忍者小队的工会组织”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/fb6b60de54291f6801952a44db8f47c4.poster.avif?t=1769712918\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/fb6b60de54291f6801952a44db8f47c4.webm?t=1769712918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/fb6b60de54291f6801952a44db8f47c4.mp4?t=1769712918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具体而言：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 经典而精细的潜行机制——搭载可见性与噪音侦测系统（实现“暗影潜行”体验，同时避免“眼前一抹黑”的困扰）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 智能化的敌人会对你的行动作出反应——例如察觉敞开的房门，且不同类型的敌人会采取各自独特的应对方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 多路径关卡设计——隐藏路线、立体空间结构与灵活的通关方案并存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 可交互的世界：巧妙利用环境要素——用道具分散注意力、侵入电脑系统、发掘隐藏秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 非致命与致命工具组合：配备电击枪、枪械、近战武器、投掷物（包括橡胶猪玩偶等特殊道具）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 玩家自主掌控节奏——既可缓慢缜密地渗透，也能展开快节奏的混乱突围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/bf41d5e22b5c2fe2511bb7d6de5fe0d5.poster.avif?t=1769712918\" width=920 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/bf41d5e22b5c2fe2511bb7d6de5fe0d5.webm?t=1769712918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285390/extras/bf41d5e22b5c2fe2511bb7d6de5fe0d5.mp4?t=1769712918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
